item.title: 100errors how to fix only for pro
item.dc:creator: @x_spike_x x spike x
item.description:
@x_spike_x wrote:

This has nothing to do with mysql, it’s in your client.java, where it says illegal start of expression, then a sub procedure is not correct, so where ever the error is, in this case search for:

else(true) goto _L2;

It is likely that there could be simple error like a capital letter or spelling mistake, or you may not have closed a procedure using the scope “}”.
